[30;1m31 | [0m[35m        of the inner ‘g’ (i.e., the circle and triangle) are not part of the inner ‘g’ element's [0m
[30;1m32 | [0m[35m        background and because ShiftBGAndBlur ignores SourceGraphic, the children of the inner ‘g’[0m
[30;1m33 | [0m[35m        do not appear in the result.[0m

[30;1m33 | [0m[35m        center for the from and to values is 0, 0. At 0 seconds, the[0m
